node.text: Bust Cherry Tomato Sauce-a simple, fresh tomato sauce made with cherry tomatoes, olive oil, garlic, and basil. Enjoy with pasta, spaghetti squash, zoodles, bread, or put it on veggies or eggs! It’s so simple and so good! Click @twopeasandpod for the recipe link!🍅❤️ https://www.twopeasandtheirpod.com/burst-cherry-tomato-sauce/ #twopeasandtheirpod 📷 @theoliveandmango

node.text: It’s Friday and I think we all need a treat! Make my easy No-Bake Scotcheroos! These bars have all of my favorites-peanut butter, chocolate, and butterscotch! The combo is crazy delicious! Find the recipe on our blog! https://www.twopeasandtheirpod.com/scotcheroos/ #twopeasandtheirpod

node.text: Blueberry Peach Crumble-juicy blueberries and sweet peaches are covered in a buttery oat topping and baked until bubbly. This is the perfect fruit dessert for summertime. And if you ask me it’s perfectly acceptable for breakfast too!😍 Click @twopeasandpod for the recipe link!🫐🍑 https://www.twopeasandtheirpod.com/blueberry-peach-crumble/ #twopeasandtheirpod 📷 @bakedambrosia

node.text:
🎉GIVEAWAY🎉 UPDATE: The giveaway is closed! The winners are: @acduke @grayson_nation_  @carolyn_leigh96 
Today, I am teaming up with some of my favorite friends: @skinnytaste @howsweeteats @grandbabycakes AND @theoriginalgreenpan for a special giveaway! YAY! 

We are giving away the Venice Pro Ceramic 10-Piece Cookware Set. The stainless steel pans are GORGEOUS, plus they are safe for all cooking surfaces (and ovens). The pans heat evenly, are great for healthy cooking, and are easy to clean! You will love them! 

We are picking THREE Winners! Oh, and we are also throwing in copies of ALL of our cookbooks! So each winner will get 4 cookbooks and the pans!💯

To enter:
1. Like this photo
2. Follow @twopeasandpod @skinnytaste @howsweeteats @grandbabycakes & @theoriginalgreenpan (must follow ALL accounts)
3. Tag your friends (1 comment = 1 entry)

Giveaway closes Friday, August 20th. This giveaway is not associated with Instagram! U.S. residents only. Good luck!

node.text: This is a fun summer pizza that is located with flavor! It has chorizo, fresh sweet corn, garlic, lots of cheese, green onion, and candied jalapeños. We always garnish with cilantro and avocado slices because why not? Click @twopeasandpod for the recipe link! You need to try it!🌽 https://www.twopeasandtheirpod.com/chorizo-corn-pizza/ #twopeasandtheirpod 📷 @theoliveandmango

node.text:
Exciting news!🎉

We teamed up with @hiresbigh to create a Salted Malted Chocolate Chip Cookie Milkshake!  The shake has vanilla ice cream, lots of our freshly baked cookies, and Hire’s famous salted caramel sauce! Yep, it’s AMAZING!😋

The shake is available this week (Monday-Saturday) at all Hires locations! If you live in Utah, you have to try it! Tag me and let me know what you think! We are going tonight and maybe every night! It’s that good!💯 #twopeasandtheirpod
